variations.name: Skinny Taper Fit Men's Jeans
variations.description:
These Skinny Taper jeans look like a skinny without feeling like one, thanks to innovative stretch technology. (Levi's® Flex is engineered to deliver maximum flex and comfort.) Plus, the modern tapering gives you that put-together look—without the trip to a tailor.

  • Skinny, tapered jeans with added stretch
  • Narrow leg opening for a truly modern silhouette
  • Made with Levi's® Flex Eco Performance, our advanced stretch technology engineered from natural fibers, for maximum flex and comfort
  • We made this garment with TENCEL™ Lyocell, a soft fiber sourced from wood

These Skinny Taper jeans look like a skinny without feeling like one, thanks to innovative stretch technology. (Levi's® Flex is engineered to deliver maximum flex and comfort.) Plus, the modern tapering gives you that put-together look—without the trip to a tailor.

  • Skinny, tapered jeans with added stretch
  • Narrow leg opening for a truly modern silhouette
  • Made with Levi's® Flex Eco Performance, our advanced stretch technology engineered from natural fibers, for maximum flex and comfort
  • We made this garment with TENCEL™ Lyocell, a soft fiber sourced from wood

These jeans look like a skinny without feeling like one, thanks to innovative stretch technology. (Levi's® Flex is engineered to deliver maximum flex and comfort.) Plus, the modern tapering gives you that put-together look—without the trip to a tailor. Feel-good bonus: We made these with TENCEL™ Lyocell, a soft fiber sourced from wood.

  • A skinny, tapered jean with added stretch
  • Narrow leg opening for a truly modern silhouette
  • Made with +Levi's® Flex Eco Performance, our advanced stretch technology engineered from sustainably harvested fibers, for maximum flex and comfort
  • We made this garment with TENCEL™ Lyocell, a soft fiber sourced from sustainably harvested wood

metadata.feature-fit_text: Front rise: 10"|Knee: 14 1/2"|Leg Opening: 11 1/2"|Measurements based on size 32.|Model is 6' 3" with a 30" waist. They're wearing a size 30" x 32".|Sits at the Waist|Skinny|Slim Through The Seat And Thigh
